metadata.name: Autumn Falls
metadata.description:
Autumn Falls & Infrared Falls are the 1 of 1 photographs used to create Shades of Autumn. 

The source photo, Autumn Falls, was taken by ParraDeSys at Stony Kill Falls in Upstate, NY on October 9, 2021. 

Infrared Falls is the infrared edit from the original source photo. 

Shades of Autumn is a 1 of 1 cinemagraph that uses photographic color transitions and infrared light filters.
